<section class="what-steadro-does">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-heading">What Steadro Does</h2>
    <h3 class="section-subheading">Your Fractional Ecommerce Platform Leader</h3>
    <p class="section-body">
      Steadro steps in as the experienced operator who owns your ecommerce platform end-to-end and makes sure it can scale cleanly without chaos.
    </p>
    <ul class="responsibilities">
      <li>Stabilizes your Shopify ecosystem</li>
      <li>Removes tech debt and unnecessary complexity</li>
      <li>Aligns apps, integrations, and workflows</li>
      <li>Builds lifecycle marketing foundations (email/SMS)</li>
      <li>Owns roadmap, prioritization, and technical decisions</li>
      <li>Ensures your platform can scale cleanly to $5M and beyond</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="outcome">
      The result: a calm, organized, scalable ecommerce operation—finally.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
  .what-steadro-does {
    padding: 4rem 24px;
    background-color: var(--bg-primary);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .section-heading {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .section-subheading {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .section-body {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .responsibilities {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .responsibilities li {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  .responsibilities li:before {
    content: "✓";
    color: var(--success);
    font-weight: bold;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }
  .outcome {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-heading {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .responsibilities {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

